prediction.sparql:
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?university ?universityLabel WHERE {
  wd:Q76 wdt:P69 ?university .
  ?university rdfs:label ?universityLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?universityLabel ) = 'en' ) .
  FILTER ( CONTAINS( LCASE( ?universityLabel ) , 'university' ) || CONTAINS( LCASE( ?universityLabel ) , 'college' ) ) FILTER ( ?university != wd:Q6411346 )
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
SELECT ?senator ?senatorLabel ?start ?end WHERE {
  ?senator wdt:P39 ?position .
  ?position wdt:P31 wd:Q486282 .
  ?position wdt:P1029 wd:Q1370 .
  ?position pq:P580 ?start .
  ?position pq:P582 ?end .
  FILTER ( ?start <= "2013-12-31" ^^ xsd:date && ?end >= "2013-01-01" ^^ xsd:date ) OPTIONAL {
    ?senator rdfs:label ?senatorLabel .
    FILTER ( LANG( ?senatorLabel ) = "en" )
  }
}

PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
SELECT ?coach WHERE {
  wd:Q330120 p:P286 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P286 ?coach .
  ?statement pq:P580 ?start .
  ?statement pq:P582 ?end .
  FILTER ( ?start <= '2013-12-31' ^^ xsd:date && ?end >= '2013-01-01' ^^ xsd:date )
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?laos ?laosLabel ?coordinates WHERE {
  wd:Q819 rdfs:label ?laosLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?laosLabel ) = "en" ) wd:Q819 wdt:P625 ?coordinates .
  BIND( wd:Q819 AS ?laos )
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
SELECT ?voiceActor ?startDate WHERE {
  wd:Q908772 p:P725 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P725 ?voiceActor .
  ?statement pq:P580 ?startDate
}
ORDER BY ASC ( ?startDate )
LIMIT 1

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
SELECT ?start ?end WHERE {
  wd:Q91 p:P39 [ ps:P39 wd:Q11696 ; pq:P580 ?start ; pq:P582 ?end ] .
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?city ?cityLabel ?population WHERE {
  ?city wdt:P31 wd:Q515 .
  ?city wdt:P1082 ?population .
  ?city wdt:P17 wd:Q29 .
  OPTIONAL {
    ?city rdfs:label ?cityLabel .
    FILTER ( LANG( ?cityLabel ) = "en" )
  }
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?population )
LIMIT 1

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
SELECT ?startDate WHERE {
  wd:Q33866 p:P39 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P39 wd:Q11696 .
  ?statement pq:P580 ?startDate .
}

PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
SELECT ?placeOfResidence ?startTime ?endTime WHERE {
  wd:Q207 wdt:P551 ?placeOfResidence .
  OPTIONAL {
    ?placeOfResidence p:P551 ?statement .
    ?statement pq:P580 ?startTime .
    ?statement pq:P582 ?endTime .
  }
  FILTER ( IF( BOUND( ?startTime ) , ?startTime <= "1964-12-31" ^^ xsd:date , true ) ) FILTER ( IF( BOUND( ?endTime ) , ?endTime >= "1946-01-01" ^^ xsd:date , true ) )
}

PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
SELECT ?vicePresident ?vicePresidentLabel WHERE {
  ?vicePresident p:P39 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P39 wd:Q11699 .
  ?statement pq:P580 ?start .
  ?statement pq:P582 ?end .
  FILTER ( ?start <= '1961-01-20T00:00:00Z' ^^ xsd:dateTime && ?end >= '1963-11-22T00:00:00Z' ^^ xsd:dateTime ) .
  OPTIONAL {
    ?vicePresident rdfs:label ?vicePresidentLabel .
    FILTER ( LANG( ?vicePresidentLabel ) = 'en' )
  }
}

PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
SELECT ?governor ?governorLabel WHERE {
  wd:Q1397 p:P6 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P6 ?governor .
  ?statement pq:P580 ?start .
  ?statement pq:P582 ?end .
  FILTER ( ?start <= "2011-12-31" ^^ xsd:dateTime && ?end >= "2011-01-01" ^^ xsd:dateTime ) .
  OPTIONAL {
    ?governor rdfs:label ?governorLabel .
    FILTER ( LANG( ?governorLabel ) = "en" )
  }
}

PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
SELECT ?primeMinister ?primeMinisterLabel ?termStart ?termEnd WHERE {
  ?primeMinister wdt:P39 wd:Q844587 .
  OPTIONAL {
    ?primeMinister rdfs:label ?primeMinisterLabel .
    FILTER ( LANG( ?primeMinisterLabel ) = "en" )
  }
  ?primeMinister p:P39 ?statement .
  ?statement pq:P580 ?termStart .
  ?statement pq:P582 ?termEnd .
  FILTER ( ?termStart <= "2011-01-01" ^^ xsd:date && ?termEnd >= "2011-12-31" ^^ xsd:date )
}
ORDER BY ?termStart
LIMIT 1

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?deity WHERE {
  wd:Q234801 rdfs:label ?label .
  BIND( wd:Q234801 AS ?deity )
}
LIMIT 1

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?country WHERE {
  wd:Q855 wdt:P39 ?position .
  ?position wdt:P1001 ?country .
  FILTER ( ?country = wd:Q15180 )
}
